Package LabBlockChain.BlockChain.Transaction

Class Transaction

java.lang.Object
LabBlockChain.BlockChain.Transaction.Transaction
public class Transaction
extends Object
Transactions that occur on a blockchain must be validated by a number of the network's participants, A transaction is only valid once the participants verify the transaction and a consensus is reached about its validity. The transaction details are then recorded on the block and distributed to the network's participants. tx- Unique ID input - > output for simplicity, here only one-to-one relationship
